ra team-up with Jimmy Fallon to throw some shade Governor Christie's way.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Meeting Across the River&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Meeting Across the River", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/meeting-across-the-river/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Bruce-Springsteen-Jimmy-Fallon.jpg?fit=1138%2C719&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Bruce-Springsteen-Jimmy-Fallon.jpg?fit=1138%2C719&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Bruce-Springsteen-Jimmy-Fallon.jpg?fit=1138%2C719&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Bruce-Springsteen-Jimmy-Fallon.jpg?fit=1138%2C719&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/Bruce-Springsteen-Jimmy-Fallon.jpg?fit=1138%2C719&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 63382, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/12/17/kingdom-of-days-december-17-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 12480, "position": 3}, "title": "Kingdom of Days: December 17", "author": "Ken", "date": "December 17, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "Bruce kicks off a multi-year tradition of Asbury Park Holiday shows. Plus: a Tonight Show appearance, last performances of several songs for years to come, and more.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/20001217_front-e1540706800117.jpg?fit=600%2C505&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/20001217_front-e1540706800117.jpg?fit=600%2C505&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/20001217_front-e1540706800117.jpg?fit=600%2C505&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 12915, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1984/02/05/cover-me-neil-young-my-hometown/", "url_meta": {"origin": 12480, "position": 4}, "title": "Neil Young: My Hometown", "author": "Ken", "date": "February 5, 1984", "format": false, "excerpt": "Certainly one of the most unusual Bruce covers, Neil Young's version of \"My Hometown\" was recorded in a vintage Voice-o-Graph recording booth. Listen to it inside, and watch Neil and Jack White discuss the project.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;BITUSA&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "BITUSA", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/bitusa/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/admin-ajax-54.jpg?fit=1200%2C994&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/admin-ajax-54.jpg?fit=1200%2C994&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/admin-ajax-54.jpg?fit=1200%2C994&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/admin-ajax-54.jpg?fit=1200%2C994&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/admin-ajax-54.jpg?fit=1200%2C994&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}, {"id": 61268, "url": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/2025/11/02/kingdom-of-days-november-2-2/", "url_meta": {"origin": 12480, "position": 5}, "title": "Kingdom of Days: November 2", "author": "Ken", "date": "November 2, 2025", "format": false, "excerpt": "On this date: \"Working on a Dream\" makes its debut, Bruce headlines a Hurricane Sandy telethon, and the first of several Seeger Sessions. More highlights inside.", "rel": "", "context": "In &quot;Kingdom of Days&quot;", "block_context": {"text": "Kingdom of Days", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/category/kingdom-of-days/"}, "img": {"alt_text": "", "src": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/20121102_2_front.jpg?fit=1200%2C1198&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200", "width": 350, "height": 200, "srcset": "https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/20121102_2_front.jpg?fit=1200%2C1198&ssl=1&resize=350%2C200 1x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/20121102_2_front.jpg?fit=1200%2C1198&ssl=1&resize=525%2C300 1.5x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/20121102_2_front.jpg?fit=1200%2C1198&ssl=1&resize=700%2C400 2x, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/20121102_2_front.jpg?fit=1200%2C1198&ssl=1&resize=1050%2C600 3x"}, "classes": []}], "_links": {"self": [{"href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/12480", "targetHints": {"allow": ["GET"]}}], "collection": [{"href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/posts"}], "about": [{"href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/types/post"}], "author": [{"embeddable": true, "href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/users/1"}], "replies": [{"embeddable": true, "href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/comments?post=12480"}], "version-history": [{"count": 8, "href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/12480/revisions"}], "predecessor-version": [{"id": 69836, "href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/12480/revisions/69836"}], "wp:featuredmedia": [{"embeddable": true, "href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/media/69835"}], "wp:attachment": [{"href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=12480"}], "wp:term": [{"taxonomy": "category", "embeddable": true, "href": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/wp-json/wp/v2/categories?post=12480"